The Trial Chamber has reclassified the expert reports regarding IENG Thirith's health in order to provide the public with a fuller understanding of the issues underlying the experts' diagnosis of dementia (likely caused by Alzheimer's disease). 
In light of paragraph 3 of the 29 August 2012 report, the Trial Chamber consulted with the court-appoint medical experts prior to this reclassification. 
The Trial Chamber previously reclassified a medical report after it was discussed in depth at the hearing on IENG Thirith's fitness in August 2012.